      • ACTION_VIEW_IPCALL

        public static final java.lang.String ACTION_VIEW_IPCALL
        Load the IP call application to view a call. This Intent takes into parameter an URI on the call (i.e. content://ipcalls/ipcall_ID). If no parameter found the main entry of the IP call application is displayed.

      • ACTION_INITIATE_IPCALL

        public static final java.lang.String ACTION_INITIATE_IPCALL
        Load the IP call application to start a new call to a given contact. This Intent takes into parameter a contact URI (i.e. content://contacts/people/contact_ID). If no parameter the main entry of the IP call application is displayed.
